divs: Sighting DetailsI noticed lots of fighter style jets all going towards one area in the sky. That is when i got a couple of the pictures, i was just trying to get all the jets into one pic, there were probably 6 or more. I think my pictures only show a couple though. I have 9 pictures in all! Only seen a flash in the sky, never seen the craft or whatever it was until i was able to study the still images.
